<body>
    <h1>2026-03-12 SRE Agent MCP Server Tools</h1>
    <div class=3D"Section1">
        <div class=3D"confluence-information-macro confluence-information-m=
acro-information">
<span class=3D"aui-icon aui-icon-small aui-iconfont-info confluence-informa=
tion-macro-icon"></span>
<div class=3D"confluence-information-macro-body">
<p local-id=3D"208a5c460754">This document lists tools available to the SRE=
 agent organized by MCP server. It includes exact queries, data sourcing, a=
nd service URLs that are accurate as of 2026-03-12. There is a current work=
 in progress for <a class=3D"external-link" href=3D"https://source.datanerd=
.us/Alerting/sre-agent-mcp-server/pull/530" rel=3D"nofollow">SRE MCP</a> an=
d <a class=3D"external-link" href=3D"https://source.datanerd.us/Alerting/ch=
ange-analyzer/pull/139" rel=3D"nofollow">Change Analyzer</a> to fully migra=
te all NRDB queries to be performed via NerdGraph instead of via <code>inte=
rnal-dirac</code>.</p>
</div>
</div>
<h4 local-id=3D"c6c549b4556d" id=3D"id-2026-03-12SREAgentMCPServerTools-Rep=
os"><strong>Repos</strong></h4>
<ul local-id=3D"84ac81a7-60af-4f7a-82f6-0de0c3b6c0de">
<li local-id=3D"6c97cc21-740e-4547-8cbf-34f8740908ff">
<p local-id=3D"f87ef33883e6"><a class=3D"external-link" href=3D"https://sou=
rce.datanerd.us/Alerting/sre-orchestration-service" rel=3D"nofollow">sre-or=
chestration-service</a> =E2=80=94 Orchestration layer + agent/tool configs<=
/p></li>
<li local-id=3D"e38fd758-b405-4620-9378-df604e499eaa">
<p local-id=3D"cb86075f9e7c"><a class=3D"external-link" href=3D"https://sou=
rce.datanerd.us/Alerting/sre-agent" rel=3D"nofollow">sre-agent-mcp-server</=
a> =E2=80=94 SRE agent=E2=80=99s analysis, entity, utility, and remediation=
 MCP tools</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"ac358083-8da6-4f74-9302-ddc81b0c659c">
<p local-id=3D"14af098d72ae"><a class=3D"external-link" href=3D"https://sou=
rce.datanerd.us/Alerting/change-analyzer" rel=3D"nofollow">change-analyzer<=
/a> =E2=80=94 Deployment impact analysis tools</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"8c5439f8-4ba1-48e9-91f6-2f4408bbf072">
<p local-id=3D"0bd7c17013b6"><a class=3D"external-link" href=3D"https://sou=
rce.datanerd.us/AIR/mcp-server" rel=3D"nofollow">mcp-server</a> =E2=80=94 N=
ew Relic AI MCP server (change events, alert recommendations)</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"93eebafb-1b70-4632-aede-ea0f3bd82801">
<h2 local-id=3D"350ec222ec29" id=3D"id-2026-03-12SREAgentMCPServerTools-sre=
-agent-server(Analysis)">sre-agent-server (Analysis)</h2>
<p local-id=3D"3286835d1754"><strong>Config:</strong> <code>sre_agent_analy=
sis_tool:v0.0.1.json</code></p>
<p local-id=3D"b5f529e294e1"><strong>Base URL:</strong> <code>${SRE_AGENT_M=
CP_SERVER_BASE_URL}/server/analysis/mcp/</code></p>
<p local-id=3D"c4632e1eab09"></p>
<h3 local-id=3D"9006bc4191c1" id=3D"id-2026-03-12SREAgentMCPServerTools-gen=
erate_entity_error_group_reports">generate_entity_error_group_reports</h3>
<p local-id=3D"4a99d0306636">Fetches error groups from Errors Inbox, priori=
tized by user impact and current state.</p>
<ul local-id=3D"7fd21652-6622-421a-b5c4-e8b3c5ba5fdd">
<li local-id=3D"f2fd4d19-15ad-4bcb-a197-278a8d556305">
<p local-id=3D"6b62e6c59666"><strong>Data source:</strong> NerdGraph =E2=80=
=94 Errors Inbox API</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"03eef3f5-ab06-4032-89a6-84168614c6bb">
<p local-id=3D"fce987faef0c"><strong>URL:</strong> <code>${NERDGRAPH_ENDPOI=
NT}/graphql</code> (E.g. - <code>https://nerd-graph.staging-service.nr-ops.=
net/graphql</code>)</p></li>
</ul>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">query E=
rrorGroupsQuery(
  $entityGuids: [EntityGuid!]!
  $states: [ErrorsInboxErrorGroupState!]
  $timeWindow: TimeWindowInput
) {
  actor {
    errorsInbox {
      errorGroups(
        entityGuids: $entityGuids
        timeWindow: $timeWindow
        filter: { states: $states }
      ) {
        results {
          message
          eventsQuery
          firstSeenAt
          lastSeenAt
          name
          id
          issueType
          usersImpacted { totalCount }
          state
          source
          url
        }
        totalCount
      }
    }
  }
}
</pre>
</div>
</div>
<hr local-id=3D"43a6fd2c-738b-40cd-a440-4e63ba283ecd">
<h3 local-id=3D"30083c08cdd8" id=3D"id-2026-03-12SREAgentMCPServerTools-ana=
lyze_garbage_collection_metrics">analyze_garbage_collection_metrics</h3>
<p local-id=3D"8111893be585">GC and memory metrics with language-specific N=
RQL queries. Performs anomaly detection on results.</p>
<ul local-id=3D"1ac00e54-e11d-4ac8-8d30-9a5b537ac273">
<li local-id=3D"c22afadf-e308-4b40-a9bf-24beb867993c">
<p local-id=3D"1155da6dda32"><strong>Data source:</strong> Dirac (NRQL) + b=
ork-sniffer (anomaly detection)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"a3abb2df-707f-45ea-a679-04af2cd3c1cd">
<p local-id=3D"f67ed61afa0e"><strong>URL:</strong> <code>${NRDB_ENDPOINT}/a=
pi/1/query</code> (default: <code>https://nrql-query-gateway.staging-servic=
e.nr-ops.net/api/1/query</code>)</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"8a39b0c93c76"><strong>Java GC queries:</strong></p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">-- Non-=
Heap memory usage
SELECT filter(average(apm.service.java.memory.pool) * 1000 * 1000, WHERE us=
ageType =3D 'Used')
  / filter(average(apm.service.java.memory.pool) * 1000 * 1000, WHERE usage=
Type =3D 'Max') as 'Non-Heap memory usage'
FROM Metric
WHERE heapType IS NOT NULL AND heapType NOT LIKE 'Heap' AND entity.guid =3D=
 '{entity_guid}'

-- Heap memory usage
SELECT average(apm.service.memory.heap.used) / max(apm.service.memory.heap.=
max) AS 'Heap memory usage'
FROM Metric
WHERE entity.guid =3D '{entity_guid}'

-- GC CPU Time
SELECT average(newrelic.timeslice.value) as 'GC CPU Time'
FROM Metric
WHERE metricTimesliceName =3D 'GC/G1 Young Generation' AND entity.guid =3D =
'{entity_guid}'
</pre>
</div>
</div>
<p local-id=3D"428606cc6365"><strong>Go GC queries:</strong></p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">-- Paus=
e Time
SELECT average(newrelic.timeslice.value) * 1000 as 'Average', max(newrelic.=
timeslice.value) * 1000 as 'Max'
FROM Metric
WHERE entity.guid =3D '{entity_guid}' AND metricTimesliceName =3D 'GC/Syste=
m/Pauses'
FACET host

-- Pause Frequency
SELECT count(newrelic.timeslice.value) as 'Pauses'
FROM Metric
WHERE entity.guid =3D '{entity_guid}' AND metricTimesliceName =3D 'GC/Syste=
m/Pauses'
FACET host

-- Pause Time (% of wall clock time)
SELECT average(newrelic.timeslice.value) as 'Pause fraction'
FROM Metric
WHERE entity.guid =3D '{entity_guid}' AND metricTimesliceName =3D 'GC/Syste=
m/Pause Fraction'
FACET host
</pre>
</div>
</div>
<p local-id=3D"6595cd3f572f"><strong>Default GC query (other languages):</s=
trong></p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">SELECT =
sum(newrelic.timeslice.value) AS 'Sum',
       average(newrelic.timeslice.value) AS 'Average',
       count(newrelic.timeslice.value) AS 'Count'
FROM Metric
WHERE entity.guid =3D '{entity_guid}' AND metricTimesliceName LIKE 'GC/%'
FACET metricTimesliceName
</pre>
</div>
</div>
<hr local-id=3D"6d2cb4bf-fed7-4833-9773-ad25efcb04e6">
<h3 local-id=3D"377ad4113fbc" id=3D"id-2026-03-12SREAgentMCPServerTools-ana=
lyze_entity_thread_metrics">analyze_entity_thread_metrics</h3>
<p local-id=3D"602fc0e640dd">Thread state, CPU, and memory analysis. Langua=
ge-aware (Java, Go, .NET, Ruby).</p>
<ul local-id=3D"621e7eb6-fed9-4c4b-9802-be3b1b9e816a">
<li local-id=3D"6b67a1eb-8d5f-426c-af4e-0ea2ad72382b">
<p local-id=3D"13a8e5caa658"><strong>Data source:</strong> Dirac (NRQL) + b=
ork-sniffer (anomaly detection)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"77616272-da16-437c-8f56-20a7c3dc7606">
<p local-id=3D"3d125ce02a54"><strong>URL:</strong> <code>${NRDB_ENDPOINT}/a=
pi/1/query</code></p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"92d962070c6c"><strong>Generic thread queries (all languages)=
:</strong></p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">-- Bloc=
ked/Waited thread counts
SELECT sum(newrelic.timeslice.value) AS 'Threads/Count/%'
FROM Metric WITH METRIC_FORMAT 'Threads/Count/{thread}/{state}'
WHERE entity.guid =3D '{entity_guid}' AND metricTimesliceName LIKE 'Threads=
/Count/%'
  AND state IN ('BlockedCount', 'WaitedCount')
FACET host, thread, state

-- Thread summary by state
SELECT sum(newrelic.timeslice.value) AS 'Threads/SummaryState/%/Count'
FROM Metric WITH METRIC_FORMAT 'Threads/SummaryState/{state}/Count'
WHERE entity.guid =3D '{entity_guid}' AND metricTimesliceName LIKE 'Threads=
/SummaryState/%/Count'
FACET host, state

-- CPU time by thread
SELECT sum(newrelic.timeslice.value) AS 'Threads/TotalTime/%/CpuTime'
FROM Metric WITH METRIC_FORMAT 'Threads/TotalTime/{thread}/CpuTime'
WHERE entity.guid =3D '{entity_guid}' AND metricTimesliceName LIKE 'Threads=
/TotalTime/%/CpuTime'
FACET host, thread
</pre>
</div>
</div>
<p local-id=3D"0ec04471e47a"><strong>Java-specific:</strong></p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">-- Thre=
ad count
SELECT filter(average(newrelic.timeslice.value),
  where metricTimesliceName =3D 'JmxBuiltIn/Threads/Thread Count') as 'Thre=
adCount'
FROM Metric WHERE entity.guid =3D '{entity_guid}'
FACET host, `host.displayName` OR `instanceName`

-- Thread pool metrics
SELECT filter(average(newrelic.timeslice.value), where metricTimesliceName =
=3D 'JmxBuiltIn/ThreadPool/0/Max') as 'Max',
       filter(average(newrelic.timeslice.value), where metricTimesliceName =
=3D 'JmxBuiltIn/ThreadPool/0/Idle') as 'Idle',
       filter(average(newrelic.timeslice.value), where metricTimesliceName =
=3D 'JmxBuiltIn/ThreadPool/0/Active') as 'Active'
FROM Metric WHERE entity.guid =3D '{entity_guid}'
FACET host, `host.displayName` OR `instanceName`
</pre>
</div>
</div>
<p local-id=3D"61c18728363d"><strong>Go-specific:</strong></p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">SELECT =
average(newrelic.timeslice.value) AS `Go/Runtime/Goroutines`
FROM Metric
WHERE entity.guid =3D '{entity_guid}' AND metricTimesliceName =3D 'Go/Runti=
me/Goroutines'
FACET host
</pre>
</div>
</div>
<p local-id=3D"dc7676159bbe"><strong>.NET-specific:</strong></p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">-- Thre=
ad pool states
SELECT average(newrelic.timeslice.value) AS 'Worker threads'
FROM Metric WITH METRIC_FORMAT 'Threadpool/{threadPool}/{state}'
WHERE entity.guid =3D '{entity_guid}'
FACET host, threadPool, state

-- Thread throughput
SELECT average(newrelic.timeslice.value) AS 'Threads throughput'
FROM Metric WITH METRIC_FORMAT 'Threadpool/Throughput/{state}'
WHERE entity.guid =3D '{entity_guid}'
FACET host, state
</pre>
</div>
</div>
<p local-id=3D"be63dda2d092"><strong>Ruby-specific:</strong></p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">SELECT =
(filter(count(newrelic.timeslice.value), WHERE metricTimesliceName =3D 'Rub=
yVM/Threads/all')
  / count(apm.service.instance.count)) as 'Threads per Instance'
FROM Metric WHERE entity.guid =3D '{entity_guid}'
FACET host, `host.displayName` OR `instanceName`
</pre>
</div>
</div>
<hr local-id=3D"86ecf91a-02c2-46e2-b9ec-a07993e09fef">
<h3 local-id=3D"de509d4290e9" id=3D"id-2026-03-12SREAgentMCPServerTools-ana=
lyze_entity_golden_metrics">analyze_entity_golden_metrics</h3>
<p local-id=3D"f954ac195826">Golden signal analysis =E2=80=94 throughput, r=
esponse time, error rate, Apdex. Includes anomaly detection.</p>
<ul local-id=3D"9081227e-7215-4f48-a710-708916851792">
<li local-id=3D"b4855f07-3041-4dc8-b033-86fac895f31b">
<p local-id=3D"a8a333d3fbc4"><strong>Data source:</strong> Dirac (NRQL time=
series), NerdGraph (Entity Platform - golden signal definitions), bork-snif=
fer (anomalies)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"3444795c-a060-4c10-8ad9-c8b9b35f1ec8">
<p local-id=3D"a20eae79e17b"><strong>URL:</strong> <code>${NRDB_ENDPOINT}/a=
pi/1/query</code></p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"3cb11ba55983">The NRQL is constructed dynamically from the e=
ntity's <code>golden_metrics.multi_nrql</code> property (fetched via the <c=
ode>EntitiesQuery</code> NerdGraph query below). The entity GUID filter is =
appended:</p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">{entity=
.golden_metrics.multi_nrql} WHERE entity.guid =3D '{entity_guid}'</pre>
</div>
</div>
<p local-id=3D"faa66100f8c7">The golden metrics definition comes from this =
NerdGraph query (<code>entities.graphql</code>):</p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">query E=
ntitiesQuery($guids: [EntityGuid]!) {
  actor {
    entities(guids: $guids) {
      goldenMetrics {
        metrics {
          name
          unit
          definition { select, from, where, facet }
        }
      }
    }
  }
}</pre>
</div>
</div>
<hr local-id=3D"394103fd-a48e-401b-99fc-90c70e9124a1">
<h3 local-id=3D"8fe0649507d7" id=3D"id-2026-03-12SREAgentMCPServerTools-ana=
lyze_entity_kafka_metrics">analyze_entity_kafka_metrics</h3>
<p local-id=3D"fd8b97e481e0">Consumer lag, producer throughput, message lat=
ency, partition balance.</p>
<ul local-id=3D"c1a1c284-75fd-4ae9-8e02-ee21429863c1">
<li local-id=3D"5b83214e0b55">
<p local-id=3D"78d2e159b2cc"><strong>Data source:</strong> Dirac (NRQL), bo=
rk-sniffer (anomalies)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"c483f153-13fb-4877-8e5f-2a8946468346">
<p local-id=3D"dae67c79f321"><strong>URL:</strong> <code>${NRDB_ENDPOINT}/a=
pi/1/query</code></p></li>
</ul>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">-- Prod=
ucer and consumer metrics
SELECT average(`producer-metrics.request-rate`) as ProducerRequestRate,
       average(`producer-metrics.request-latency-avg`) as ProducerRequestLa=
tency,
       average(`producer-metrics.io-wait-time-ns-avg`) as ProducerIoWaitTim=
e,
       average(`consumer-fetch-manager-metrics.records-consumed-rate`) as C=
onsumerRecordsConsumedRate,
       average(`consumer-fetch-manager-metrics.fetch-latency-avg`) as Consu=
merFetchLatency,
       average(`consumer-metrics.io-ratio`) as ConsumerIoRatio,
       average(`consumer-metrics.time-between-poll-avg`) as ConsumerTimeBet=
weenPoll
FROM KafkaMetrics
WHERE entityGuid =3D '{entity_guid}'
FACET clusterName

-- Internal Kafka metrics (timeslice-based)
SELECT filter(average(newrelic.timeslice.value), WHERE
    (type =3D 'producer' AND metric =3D 'request-rate') OR
    (type =3D 'producer' AND metric =3D 'request-latency-avg') OR
    (type =3D 'consumer-fetch-manager' AND metric =3D 'records-consumed-rat=
e') OR
    (type =3D 'consumer-fetch-manager' AND metric =3D 'fetch-latency-avg') =
OR
    (type =3D 'producer' AND metric =3D 'io-wait-time-ns-avg') OR
    (type =3D 'consumer' AND metric =3D 'io-ratio') OR
    (type =3D 'consumer' AND metric =3D 'time-between-poll-avg')
  ) AS filteredMetrics
FROM Metric
WHERE entityGuid =3D '{entity_guid}'
WITH METRIC_FORMAT 'Custom/KafkaClients/{type}-metrics/client/{clientId}/{m=
etric}'
FACET type, clientId, metric

-- External Kafka metrics (MessageBroker-based)
SELECT filter(average(newrelic.timeslice.value), WHERE
    (type =3D 'producer' AND metric =3D 'request-rate') OR
    (type =3D 'consumer-fetch-manager' AND metric =3D 'records-consumed-rat=
e') OR
    ...same filter set...
  ) AS filteredMetrics
FROM Metric
WHERE entityGuid =3D '{entity_guid}'
WITH METRIC_FORMAT 'MessageBroker/Kafka/Internal/{type}-metrics/client/{cli=
entId}/{metric}'
FACET type, clientId, metric

-- Consumer lag (CLM)
SELECT max(secondsLag) as maxSecondsLag, max(offsetLag) as maxOffsetLag
FROM KafkaConsumerLag
WHERE {dynamic_where_clause}
FACET group, consumerId, topic, topicPartition</pre>
</div>
</div>
<hr local-id=3D"77675b9e-0fa6-493e-a8b8-5bd25e0de6ad">
<h3 local-id=3D"84d6a7cc8ff0" id=3D"id-2026-03-12SREAgentMCPServerTools-ana=
lyze_entity_application_logs">analyze_entity_application_logs</h3>
<p local-id=3D"984389c6d66e">Log error pattern detection and anomaly identi=
fication. Max query window: 24 hours.</p>
<ul local-id=3D"80c3c2bc-64e6-466a-93a4-8512d286a6a3">
<li local-id=3D"c7ed978b-c336-4346-ba6e-e64b2e07d218">
<p local-id=3D"00b63c47410c"><strong>Data source:</strong> Dirac (NRQL)</p>=
</li>
<li local-id=3D"aeaf551f-8265-43e7-aef3-e3d043b3da1f">
<p local-id=3D"28497dcc915e"><strong>URL:</strong> <code>${NRDB_ENDPOINT}/a=
pi/1/query</code></p></li>
</ul>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">SELECT =
* FROM Log WHERE entity.guid =3D '{entity_guid}'</pre>
</div>
</div>
<hr local-id=3D"4ff81dee-6f4c-4228-a134-d73344809cf2">
<h3 local-id=3D"1f99ae0e14b4" id=3D"id-2026-03-12SREAgentMCPServerTools-lis=
t_top_transactions">list_top_transactions</h3>
<p local-id=3D"4b3ef81cd341">Top transactions ranked by configurable criter=
ia.</p>
<ul local-id=3D"2c509c62-09c9-4993-9000-e0515ca48a30">
<li local-id=3D"a097c8ce-c96a-48a6-a504-500a51c6d93e">
<p local-id=3D"cac6523c90a0"><strong>Data source:</strong> Dirac (NRQL)</p>=
</li>
<li local-id=3D"7cbf48c8-d59f-433a-b580-636ddd8a4e33">
<p local-id=3D"6dbffbe438b5"><strong>URL:</strong> <code>${NRDB_ENDPOINT}/a=
pi/1/query</code></p></li>
</ul>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">-- "mos=
t time consuming" (default)
SELECT rate(sum(apm.service.transaction.duration), 1 minute) FROM Metric WH=
ERE entityGuid =3D '{entity_guid}' FACET transactionName

-- "slowest average response time"
SELECT average(convert(apm.service.transaction.duration, unit, 'ms')) FROM =
Metric WHERE entityGuid =3D '{entity_guid}' FACET transactionName

-- "highest error rate"
SELECT clamp_max(count(apm.service.transaction.error.count) / count(apm.ser=
vice.transaction.duration), 1) FROM Metric WHERE entityGuid =3D '{entity_gu=
id}' FACET transactionName

-- "throughput"
SELECT rate(count(apm.service.transaction.duration), 1 minute) FROM Metric =
WHERE entityGuid =3D '{entity_guid}' FACET transactionName

-- "apdex"
SELECT apdex(apm.service.transaction.apdex) FROM Metric WHERE entityGuid =
=3D '{entity_guid}' FACET transactionName
</pre>
</div>
</div>
<hr local-id=3D"cb3d8bc0-152f-4ac0-b76b-bd74fd107bad">
<h3 local-id=3D"2e9199e0770f" id=3D"id-2026-03-12SREAgentMCPServerTools-get=
_transaction_analysis">get_transaction_analysis</h3>
<p local-id=3D"81e8e7ccc0ad">Overview metrics: total count, avg duration, p=
95, error rate, throughput/min.</p>
<ul local-id=3D"ed653e34-ffb4-423c-a91e-25b21724f929">
<li local-id=3D"60ce80ba-acc7-4620-88a0-21f8852d36f4">
<p local-id=3D"1e0566ce8bb8"><strong>Data source:</strong> Dirac (NRQL) + b=
ork-sniffer (anomaly detection)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"e68583b7-5e81-4378-9b0d-c685880a7b3b">
<p local-id=3D"9aac1fb47ff6"><strong>URL:</strong> <code>${NRDB_ENDPOINT}/a=
pi/1/query</code></p></li>
</ul>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">-- Over=
view (Metric event type)
SELECT count(apm.service.transaction.duration) as 'count',
       average(apm.service.transaction.duration) as 'average.duration',
       percentile(apm.service.transaction.duration, 95) as 'percentile.dura=
tion',
       sum(apm.service.error.count['count']) / count(apm.service.transactio=
n.duration) as 'Error Rate %',
       rate(count(apm.service.transaction.duration), 1 minute) as 'Throughp=
ut per min'
FROM Metric WHERE entity.guid =3D '{entity_guid}'

-- Error transactions (Transaction event type)
SELECT count(*) as 'count',
       average(duration) as 'average.duration',
       percentile(duration, 95) as 'percentile.duration',
       percentage(count(*), WHERE error is true) as 'Error Rate %',
       rate(count(*), 1 minute) as 'Throughput per min'
FROM Transaction
WHERE entityGuid =3D '{entity_guid}' AND error IS true
ORDER BY timestamp DESC
</pre>
</div>
</div>
<hr local-id=3D"051a2ddb-52ad-4f92-8913-c8702c656e43">
<h3 local-id=3D"5f934c9dfb01" id=3D"id-2026-03-12SREAgentMCPServerTools-get=
_alerts_by_entity_guid">get_alerts_by_entity_guid</h3>
