</div>
<hr local-id=3D"fbdebb53-9473-43a7-81c2-0919399f4a8b">
<h3 local-id=3D"397b3fd4b390" id=3D"id-2026-03-12SREAgentMCPServerTools-get=
_alerts_by_issue_id">get_alerts_by_issue_id</h3>
<p local-id=3D"e1e6ab0dd337">Alert incidents associated with a specific iss=
ue. Two-step query: resolves issue =E2=86=92 incidents =E2=86=92 events.</p=
>
<ul local-id=3D"904671bc-a1a6-47f6-8c34-d65c87689fb5">
<li local-id=3D"c9f0d971-ffde-4521-82f3-2e28f34afa59">
<p local-id=3D"0f7d631b5e73"><strong>Data source:</strong> NerdGraph (NRQL =
via NerdGraph wrapper)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"71cd8803-c052-4b97-9c69-b9b525fb1744">
<p local-id=3D"c69d24fe43a8"><strong>URL:</strong> <code>${NERDGRAPH_ENDPOI=
NT}/graphql</code></p></li>
</ul>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">-- Step=
 1: Resolve incident IDs from issue
SELECT incidentIds FROM NrAiIssue WHERE issueId =3D '{issue_id}'

-- Step 2: Fetch alert events (same SELECT as get_alerts_by_entity_guid)
SELECT policyId, policyName, conditionId, conditionName, title, targetName,
       nrqlQuery, nrqlEventType, event, incidentId, incidentLink, runbookUr=
l
FROM NrAiIncident
WHERE incidentId IN ({resolved_incident_ids})</pre>
</div>
</div>
<hr local-id=3D"6364766b-2610-468f-af9b-3bf5448af76a">
<h3 local-id=3D"bfab2b484fd4" id=3D"id-2026-03-12SREAgentMCPServerTools-get=
_alerts_by_policy_condition_ids">get_alerts_by_policy_condition_ids</h3>
