<p local-id=3D"ba18a343e67e"><strong>Data source:</strong> NerdGraph (NRQL =
via NerdGraph wrapper)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"4c1c1a1e-c854-4db4-9bb2-42e1528f335d">
<p local-id=3D"8db5b968150e"><strong>URL:</strong> <code>${NERDGRAPH_ENDPOI=
NT}/graphql</code></p></li>
