<hr local-id=3D"ff8f8fe2-0641-4fe5-bf14-11bace3c8f90">
<h3 local-id=3D"14109b2e0ae0" id=3D"id-2026-03-12SREAgentMCPServerTools-get=
_entity_trace_call_graph">get_entity_trace_call_graph</h3>
<p local-id=3D"a07031d1b49a">Distributed tracing call graph showing upstrea=
m/downstream dependencies. Returns visualization URL.</p>
