</li>
</ul>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">{
  "durationMs": 1200000,
  "entityGuid": "{entity_guid}",
  "startTimeMs": "{start_time_ms}",
  "limit": 100,
  "filter": {}
}
</pre>
</div>
</div>
<hr local-id=3D"13cd9414-874b-4fe5-bad9-8d57257b0902">
<h3 local-id=3D"19f1052a5bb2" id=3D"id-2026-03-12SREAgentMCPServerTools-int=
elligent_causal_analysis">intelligent_causal_analysis</h3>
<p local-id=3D"1f34138b7a25">Graph-based root cause analysis on a New Relic=
 issue. Returns ranked causes with confidence scores.</p>
<ul local-id=3D"dd0fb14b-6580-4c07-9ee5-a69547a42730">
<li local-id=3D"c4626b19-a246-4ef0-852f-b09d462faf18">
<p local-id=3D"645861d5523a"><strong>Data source:</strong> <a class=3D"exte=
rnal-link" href=3D"https://source.datanerd.us/causal-engine" rel=3D"nofollo=
w">causal-engine</a> (REST API)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"6ff867bd-87f5-468c-9745-3c7accac770c">
<p local-id=3D"5da383ec0a6c"><strong>URL:</strong> <code>${IRCA_ENDPOINT}/v=
1/causal-analysis</code> (default: <code>https://causal-engine.staging-serv=
ice.nr-ops.net/v1/causal-analysis</code>)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"c5ef3065-db27-43ed-a6dd-956b42ceb5d3">
<p local-id=3D"f69237e71dce"><strong>Method:</strong> <code>POST</code></p>=
</li>
</ul>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">{
  "accountId": "{issue_account_id}",
  "issueId": "{issue_id}",
  "entityId": "{entity_guid}",
  "issueStartTimeMs": "{start_time_ms}",
  "maxDepth": 3
}
</pre>
</div>
</div>
<hr local-id=3D"75b8169d-cfca-48a0-b652-f4b9ef632147">
<h3 local-id=3D"7ece9694ea1e" id=3D"id-2026-03-12SREAgentMCPServerTools-cau=
sal_analysis">causal_analysis</h3>
<p local-id=3D"f27df42eda83">Comprehensive RCA that orchestrates <strong>3 =
parallel analysis tasks</strong> across multiple external services, gated b=
y feature flags. Combines NRQL-based analysis, graph-based intelligent RCA,=
 and entity relationship traversal with anomaly detection.</p>
<h4 local-id=3D"6ae12c797301" id=3D"id-2026-03-12SREAgentMCPServerTools-Cal=
lFlow">Call Flow</h4>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">causal_=
analysis()
=E2=94=82
=E2=94=9C=E2=94=80=E2=86=92 featureflag-api (check 3 flags)
=E2=94=82
=E2=94=9C=E2=94=80=E2=86=92 Task 1: entity_relationship_analysis()
=E2=94=82   =E2=94=9C=E2=94=80=E2=86=92 NerdGraph (entity_relationship_trav=
ersal query)
=E2=94=82   =E2=94=9C=E2=94=80=E2=86=92 traverse_causal_graph()
=E2=94=82   =E2=94=82   =E2=94=9C=E2=94=80=E2=86=92 Dirac (NRQL golden metr=
ics per entity)
=E2=94=82   =E2=94=82   =E2=94=9C=E2=94=80=E2=86=92 bork-sniffer (anomaly d=
etection on timeseries)
=E2=94=82   =E2=94=82   =E2=94=94=E2=94=80=E2=86=92 Pearson correlation ana=
lysis (local)
=E2=94=82   =E2=94=94=E2=94=80 Returns: CausalGraphCandidate objects
=E2=94=82
=E2=94=9C=E2=94=80=E2=86=92 Task 2: perform_causal_analysis()
=E2=94=82   =E2=94=94=E2=94=80=E2=86=92 root-causeinator-api (/api/v4/rca)
=E2=94=82
=E2=94=94=E2=94=80=E2=86=92 Task 3: run_irca_graph_analysis()
    =E2=94=94=E2=94=80=E2=86=92 causal-engine (/v1/causal-analysis)
</pre>
</div>
</div>
<p local-id=3D"5c9cffbfad2e">All 3 tasks run concurrently gated by feature =
flags (<code>entity_relationship_analysis</code>, <code>sre_causal_analysis=
</code>, <code>intelligent_causal_analysis</code>).</p>
<h4 local-id=3D"ab268cc87856" id=3D"id-2026-03-12SREAgentMCPServerTools-Ent=
ityRelationshipAnalysis">Entity Relationship Analysis</h4>
<p local-id=3D"976a6b642f57">Traverses entity relationships, fetches golden=
 metrics for each entity, and runs anomaly detection.</p>
<p local-id=3D"4b115057af18"><strong>Step 1 =E2=80=94 Fetch entity graph:</=
strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"307e46bcacbe">
<li local-id=3D"365d57c650fa">
<p local-id=3D"4f996c3eeda1">NerdGraph <code>EntityRelationshipTraversal</c=
ode> query (same as <code>fetch_related_entities</code>)</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"d7b786462ddc"><strong>Step 2 =E2=80=94 Fetch golden metrics =
per entity:</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"5406ea1bdba9">
<li local-id=3D"b38eb4de4134">
<p local-id=3D"9687b6ebe6b9"><strong>Source</strong>: Dirac (NRQL)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"73f4fdfa267a">
<p local-id=3D"a65cd3b2c155"><strong>URL:</strong> <code>${NRDB_ENDPOINT}/a=
pi/1/query</code></p></li>
<li local-id=3D"95e5f9e2f347">
<p local-id=3D"38d937e4b3de">Uses each entity's <code>golden_metrics</code>=
 definition</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"110b403b3cf5"><strong>Step 3 =E2=80=94 Anomaly detection:</s=
trong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"0cb40266fc25">
<li local-id=3D"664ab0557b89">
<p local-id=3D"312cf272174a"><strong>Source</strong>: <a class=3D"external-=
link" href=3D"https://source.datanerd.us/bork-sniffer/bork-sniffer" rel=3D"=
nofollow">bork-sniffer</a> (REST API)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"e01f003e-7633-41d2-b0b6-2ed221d7ec9f">
<p local-id=3D"f18b777ad9fe"><strong>URL:</strong> <code>${ANOMALY_DETECTIO=
N_ENDPOINT}/v5/anomaly-detection</code> (default: <code>https://bork-sniffe=
r.staging-service.nr-ops.net/v5/anomaly-detection</code>)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"bed6799c-a14c-4880-a03c-21d78ec12853">
<p local-id=3D"38850f581694"><strong>Method:</strong> <code>POST</code></p>=
</li>
</ul>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">{
  "timeSeries": [
    {
      "id": "{metric_name}",
      "trainingData": [
        { "value": 0.0, "beginTimeMillis": 0, "endTimeMillis": 0 }
      ],
      "evaluationData": [
        { "value": 0.0, "beginTimeMillis": 0, "endTimeMillis": 0 }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "anomalyWindowSize": "{window_size}",
  "anomalyOccurrenceThreshold": "{threshold}"
}
</pre>
</div>
</div>
<p local-id=3D"a3fe85ba1d0f"><strong>Step 4 =E2=80=94 Correlation:</strong>=
 Local Pearson correlation analysis across anomalous metrics to identify ca=
usal relationships.</p>
<h4 local-id=3D"db2928712ca5" id=3D"id-2026-03-12SREAgentMCPServerTools-Tas=
k2:NRQL-basedRCA">Task 2: NRQL-based RCA</h4>
<p local-id=3D"151ea956c57e">Sends user-supplied NRQL query to root-causein=
ator for focused analysis.</p>
<ul local-id=3D"578c9945-cd60-4ec9-8d32-9524dc7da21b">
<li local-id=3D"a6f232d8-acf9-4085-aee7-a2865860dda2">
<p local-id=3D"611ce585a5c3"><strong>Service:</strong> <a class=3D"external=
-link" href=3D"https://source.datanerd.us/root-causeinator/root-causeinator=
-api" rel=3D"nofollow">root-causeinator</a> (REST API)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"bc1776c6-1d7d-4466-85c1-5f1072b24cdc">
<p local-id=3D"90b6e1556dd8"><strong>URL:</strong> <code>${CAUSAL_ANALYSIS_=
ENDPOINT}/api/v4/rca</code> (default: <code>https://root-causeinator-api.st=
aging-service.newrelic.com/api/v4/rca</code>)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"4cdb03c3-098c-4849-812c-37c0deca09ff">
<p local-id=3D"37221290d5b5"><strong>Method:</strong> <code>POST</code></p>=
</li>
</ul>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">{
  "guid": "{entity_guid}",
  "focus": {
    "type": "NRQL",
    "nrql": "{user_supplied_nrql}",
    "facet": []
  },
  "timeWindow": {
    "startTimeMs": "{start_time_ms}",
    "endTimeMs": "{end_time_ms}"
  },
  "hops": "{hops}"
}
</pre>
</div>
</div>
<h4 local-id=3D"9b5f9ad0bb9d" id=3D"id-2026-03-12SREAgentMCPServerTools-Tas=
k3:Graph-basedIntelligentRCA">Task 3: Graph-based Intelligent RCA</h4>
<p local-id=3D"830aea63e28d">Same call as <code>intelligent_causal_analysis=
</code> =E2=80=94 delegates to causal-engine.</p>
<ul local-id=3D"08a183c8-6b0c-40c9-a346-58e6d86fbc6e">
<li local-id=3D"89efa050-8d0f-42ee-9273-f88128857e3e">
<p local-id=3D"bef9a910901a"><strong>Service:</strong> <a class=3D"external=
-link" href=3D"https://source.datanerd.us/causal-engine" rel=3D"nofollow">c=
ausal-engine</a> (REST API)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"02793551-6e2a-44ec-b8ad-50c7b6f9735f">
<p local-id=3D"6bdbb3d03769"><strong>URL:</strong> <code>${CAUSAL_ENGINE_EN=
DPOINT}/v1/causal-analysis</code> (default: <code>https://causal-engine.sta=
ging-service.nr-ops.net/v1/causal-analysis</code>)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"2cd1b8ea-63cb-40a2-b1d2-39bb29b40d77">
<p local-id=3D"2e34ddae61b0"><strong>Method:</strong> <code>POST</code></p>=
</li>
</ul>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">{
  "accountId": "{issue_account_id}",
  "issueId": "{issue_id}",
  "entityId": "{entity_guid}",
  "issueStartTimeMs": "{start_time_ms}",
  "maxDepth": 3
}
</pre>
</div>
</div>
<h4 local-id=3D"2abff0089ae2" id=3D"id-2026-03-12SREAgentMCPServerTools-Fea=
tureFlagGating">Feature Flag Gating</h4>
<ul local-id=3D"b7a80d77-1ef9-4a10-a0e0-6e6cd709970d">
<li local-id=3D"97c80f24-cd19-4058-97bd-e5d1d8e18ae7">
<p local-id=3D"4c39505df89f"><strong>Service:</strong> <a class=3D"external=
-link" href=3D"https://source.datanerd.us/featureflag/featureflag-api" rel=
=3D"nofollow">featureflag-api</a> (REST API)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"468884d1-16f7-4119-a937-1482e80da591">
<p local-id=3D"8725b7223fda"><strong>URL:</strong> <code>${FEATURE_FLAG_SER=
VICE_ENDPOINT}</code> (default: <code>https://featureflag-api.staging-servi=
ce.nr-ops.net</code>)</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"c8904c6ba405">Flags evaluated: <code>entity_relationship_ana=
lysis</code>, <code>sre_causal_analysis</code>, <code>intelligent_causal_an=
alysis</code></p>
<hr local-id=3D"17e4e574-29e0-46db-b72c-9f8b0647e191">
<h3 local-id=3D"08091f729514" id=3D"id-2026-03-12SREAgentMCPServerTools-Exc=
ludedTools">Excluded Tools</h3>
<p local-id=3D"6fcce4ac9596">These tools exist on the server but are <stron=
g>not</strong> exposed to the SRE agent:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"3f0434d6-306f-4490-b791-e5f763531285">
<li local-id=3D"628e8953-40f1-4ddb-af33-5aaf1365688e">
<p local-id=3D"6f1e6f42e17b"><code>list_entity_vulnerabilities</code></p></=
li>
<li local-id=3D"b9beabfe-6a22-41ef-8a45-e7e9c4e13c10">
<p local-id=3D"66439f45dabd"><code>forecast_metrics</code></p></li>
<li local-id=3D"3886f4ce-a397-4dfb-ab81-054dd677ddc3">
<p local-id=3D"fb0f9c57e812"><code>get_alert_incident_events</code></p></li=
>
<li local-id=3D"d2430197-2228-406a-9392-d7bd2be2e398">
<p local-id=3D"5122f83ed109"><code>analyze_otel_collector_metrics</code></p=
></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"e1ab6359-65c7-4851-8f36-3229e6c1dcfe">
<h2 local-id=3D"9370cb4d5e34" id=3D"id-2026-03-12SREAgentMCPServerTools-sre=
-agent-server(Entity)">sre-agent-server (Entity)</h2>
<p local-id=3D"5a3fcff6a31d"><strong>Config:</strong> <code>sre_agent_entit=
y_tool:v0.0.1.json</code></p>
<p local-id=3D"28530d1d43de"><strong>Base URL:</strong> <code>${SRE_AGENT_M=
CP_SERVER_BASE_URL}/server/general/mcp/</code></p>
<h3 local-id=3D"a6c333534b00" id=3D"id-2026-03-12SREAgentMCPServerTools-fet=
ch_entity">fetch_entity</h3>
<p local-id=3D"31a209081957">Lookup entities by GUID (exact) or name patter=
n (fuzzy). Supports domain/type filtering.</p>
<ul local-id=3D"a83d5fa3-7a62-48aa-b59d-76e69d219f76">
<li local-id=3D"0277ac32-3a5f-448c-aa02-3bae891ed462">
<p local-id=3D"a9ac773befa6"><strong>Data source:</strong> NerdGraph =E2=80=
=94 Entity Search API</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"9348df10-0446-4885-a4e6-e23180be6463">
<p local-id=3D"e34129efe688"><strong>URL:</strong> <code>${NERDGRAPH_ENDPOI=
NT}/graphql</code></p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"f6c11dbede18">Builds a multi-aliased GraphQL query dynamical=
ly with these search variants:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"21ee8395-0989-446c-ac82-5ee81e33ff42">
<li local-id=3D"fd3ec0af-19d3-432d-8dad-1491e7e04e0e">
<p local-id=3D"25ae064e686b"><code>exact</code>: <code>name =3D '{pattern}'=
 OR domainId =3D '{pattern}'</code></p></li>
<li local-id=3D"6c30a785-3261-4e76-ae51-c5da5882c66b">
<p local-id=3D"fb6730d6669a"><code>fuzzy</code>: <code>name LIKE '{pattern}=
'</code> (with optional domain/type)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"eade684f-c8e4-4e95-8a9c-52b14d2c308a">
<p local-id=3D"022bdbc2f020"><code>fuzzyPreferred</code>: <code>name LIKE '=
{pattern}' AND (domain IN ('APM') AND type IN ('APPLICATION') OR ...)</code=
></p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"3c6dd609718b">Entity search results fragment (<code>raw_quer=
ies.py</code>):</p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">query S=
REAgentMultiEntitySearch {
  actor {
    exact: entitySearch(query: "name =3D '{pattern}' OR domainId =3D '{patt=
ern}'") {
      results {
        entities {
          domain, permalink, name, guid, type, alertSeverity, accountId, re=
porting
          goldenMetrics {
            metrics { name, unit, definition { select, from, where, facet }=
 }
          }
          tags { key, values }
        }
      }
    }
    fuzzy: entitySearch(query: "name LIKE '{pattern}'") { ...same fragment.=
.. }
    fuzzyPreferred: entitySearch(query: "name LIKE '{pattern}' AND domain I=
N ('APM') AND type IN ('APPLICATION')") { ...same fragment... }
  }
}
</pre>
</div>
</div>
<hr local-id=3D"333cb2a7-8070-45cf-83cc-d84385d86093">
<h3 local-id=3D"2d23cea78443" id=3D"id-2026-03-12SREAgentMCPServerTools-fet=
ch_related_entities">fetch_related_entities</h3>
<p local-id=3D"091e96545404">Discovers entities 1 hop away in the relations=
hip graph.</p>
<ul local-id=3D"38221caa-3261-4b53-ac6f-bd391ac72c4b">
<li local-id=3D"b3220491-1c0b-4a8c-a995-17551178ced8">
<p local-id=3D"6532b361b750"><strong>Data source:</strong> NerdGraph =E2=80=
=94 Entity Relationship Traversal API</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"6e2f008d-369b-4a0c-b979-afc8e12b7f01">
<p local-id=3D"d3c9aa094cae"><strong>URL:</strong> <code>${NERDGRAPH_ENDPOI=
NT}/graphql</code></p></li>
</ul>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">query E=
ntityRelationshipTraversal(
  $entityGuid: EntityGuid!
  $hops: Int
  $hopFilters: [EntityRelationshipTraversalFilter!]
  $cursor: String
) {
  actor {
    entity(guid: $entityGuid) {
      accountId, domain, type, name, permalink, guid
      goldenMetrics { metrics { name, unit, definition { select, from, wher=
e, facet } } }
      tags { key, values }
      relationshipTraversal(hops: $hops, hopFilters: {default: $hopFilters}=
, cursor: $cursor) {
        nextCursor
        results {
          type
          source {
            guid
            entity { guid, name, alertSeverity, accountId, domain, type, en=
tityType, reporting, account { id, name } }
          }
          target {
            guid
            entity { guid, name, alertSeverity, accountId, domain, type, en=
tityType, reporting, account { id, name } }
          }
        }
      }
    }
  }
}
</pre>
</div>
</div>
<p local-id=3D"5efe7d35ac1a"><strong>Default exclusion filters:</strong> AI=
OPS/CONDITION, AIOPS/ISSUE, EXT/KEY_TRANSACTION, EXT/SERVICE_LEVEL, EXT/TEA=
M, NR1/WORKLOAD, REF/REPOSITORY, SYNTH/SECURE_CRED, SYNTH/PRIVATE_LOCATION,=
 VIZ/DASHBOARD</p>
<hr local-id=3D"cb98bbac-2d22-466f-b10a-6dbefa2cd326">
<h3 local-id=3D"97e44062472a" id=3D"id-2026-03-12SREAgentMCPServerTools-fet=
ch_entity_types">fetch_entity_types</h3>
<p local-id=3D"bc692af39df2">Complete catalog of New Relic entity types wit=
h domain, type, and metric definitions.</p>
<ul local-id=3D"20777912-4373-4ad7-8280-8977606e56b6">
<li local-id=3D"9640e563-b003-4c29-a92c-3fc5bcbc1c8e">
<p local-id=3D"b9e949c30a09"><strong>Data source:</strong> NerdGraph</p></l=
i>
<li local-id=3D"d410400f-8a8b-4159-b3cb-20677fe804e3">
<p local-id=3D"c92405b081d4"><strong>URL:</strong> <code>${NERDGRAPH_ENDPOI=
NT}/graphql</code></p></li>
</ul>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">query E=
ntityTypesQuery {
  actor {
    entityTypes {
      domain
      type
      summaryMetricDefinitions { title, unit }
    }
  }
}
</pre>
</div>
</div>
<hr local-id=3D"616664b4-67e0-4918-93a5-d6a673c65f3e">
<h2 local-id=3D"28dd75c58163" id=3D"id-2026-03-12SREAgentMCPServerTools-sre=
-agent-server(Utilities)">sre-agent-server (Utilities)</h2>
<p local-id=3D"b4d8c8367a99"><strong>Config:</strong> <code>sre_agent_utili=
ties_tool:v0.0.1.json</code></p>
<p local-id=3D"6f1bf891a0d6"><strong>Base URL:</strong> <code>${SRE_AGENT_M=
CP_SERVER_BASE_URL}/server/general/mcp/</code></p>
<p local-id=3D"77b54f49bf1c">Time conversion helpers. <strong>No external A=
PI calls</strong> =E2=80=94 all local processing.</p>
<h3 local-id=3D"d0d695e3fb64" id=3D"id-2026-03-12SREAgentMCPServerTools-con=
vert_time_period_to_epoch_ms">convert_time_period_to_epoch_ms</h3>
<p local-id=3D"807b52e95868">Parses natural language time expressions to ep=
och milliseconds.</p>
<ul local-id=3D"ff50edf2-6754-4bb2-a4c4-93896f7991aa">
<li local-id=3D"3da6fef9-47e9-4df8-80b3-55cb3740ff73">
<p local-id=3D"4e5effe8df42"><strong>Data source:</strong> Local NLP parsin=
g</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"304e7a83-c843-48f5-a940-4c4947269729">
<p local-id=3D"4b8872d4ac7d"><strong>Supported formats:</strong> Relative (=
"30 minutes ago"), named ("yesterday at 3pm"), ISO datetime, epoch passthro=
ugh, timezone-aware</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"dade5b45b837" id=3D"id-2026-03-12SREAgentMCPServerTools-con=
vert_epoch_ms_timestamps_to_datetime_range">convert_epoch_ms_timestamps_to_=
datetime_range</h3>
<p local-id=3D"7acd1fb90b51">Converts epoch millisecond timestamps to human=
-readable datetime strings.</p>
<ul local-id=3D"52d3221a-bc87-441c-aa68-153e0d23ebf5">
<li local-id=3D"159d9fdd-7b44-4684-bdf1-26563c93648e">
<p local-id=3D"b353b24c87d3"><strong>Data source:</strong> Local formatting=
</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"1bc89e2e-ea07-4717-8868-971bd0db68d1">
<p local-id=3D"943c556a59dd"><strong>Output format:</strong> <code>MM/DD/YY=
 HH:MM:SS</code> with timezone support (abbreviations or IANA names)</p></l=
i>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"72fb6fec-b329-4be6-a49f-47103c8f3107">
<h2 local-id=3D"7d96432e49bb" id=3D"id-2026-03-12SREAgentMCPServerTools-sre=
-agent-server(Remediation)">sre-agent-server (Remediation)</h2>
<p local-id=3D"269abbd26c20"><strong>Config:</strong> <code>sre_agent_remed=
iation_tool:v0.0.1.json</code></p>
<p local-id=3D"4ee50b35cc06"><strong>Base URL:</strong> <code>${SRE_AGENT_M=
CP_SERVER_BASE_URL}/server/remediation/mcp/</code></p>
<h3 local-id=3D"0f3aa09aa388" id=3D"id-2026-03-12SREAgentMCPServerTools-get=
_workflow_list">get_workflow_list</h3>
<p local-id=3D"e2b7ac81953d">Lists available remediation workflows for an a=
ccount. Two-step NerdGraph process.</p>
<ul local-id=3D"fd8b42f0-c716-481b-a34b-5e928f0751c6">
<li local-id=3D"ee92b68e-5019-49d8-baee-b3509046c940">
<p local-id=3D"7503f537b557"><strong>Data source:</strong> NerdGraph =E2=80=
=94 Entity Search + Workflow Automation API</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"33fa2c04-f274-495a-a4d1-06ef0c021117">
<p local-id=3D"ff402289ba80"><strong>URL:</strong> <code>${NERDGRAPH_ENDPOI=
NT}/graphql</code></p></li>
<li local-id=3D"d97d56d0-0bf4-45ac-a75a-152b5e2d126d">
<p local-id=3D"56d1dbb726f3"><strong>Query def:</strong> <code>workflows.gr=
aphql</code></p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"936b4249cf4b"><strong>Step 1: Discover workflows via entity =
search</strong></p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">query G=
etSREAgentWorkflows($query: String) {
  actor {
    entitySearch(query: $query) {
      results { entities { name } }
    }
  }
}
</pre>
</div>
</div>
<p local-id=3D"7e59c853337a">Query parameter: <code>"tags.nerdEnabled =3D '=
true' and type =3D 'WORKFLOW_AUTOMATION' and domain =3D 'WORKFLOWAUTO' and =
accountId =3D {account_id}"</code></p>
<p local-id=3D"b2e281cf4a45"><strong>Step 2: Fetch workflow details</strong=
></p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">query F=
etchWorkflowDetailsByName($accountId: Int!, $workflowName: String!) {
  actor {
    account(id: $accountId) {
      workflowAutomation {
        workflow(name: $workflowName) {
          definition { description, yaml, version, name }
        }
      }
    }
  }
}
</pre>
</div>
</div>
<hr local-id=3D"c5eb28d5-47ba-4036-bbc6-88b72666e435">
<h2 local-id=3D"45fd5b90cc22" id=3D"id-2026-03-12SREAgentMCPServerTools-cha=
nge-analyzer">change-analyzer</h2>
<p local-id=3D"4bc40b4bc318"><strong>Config:</strong> <code>change_analyzer=
_mcp_tool:v0.0.1.json</code></p>
<p local-id=3D"1d7a79e3d9db"><strong>Base URL:</strong> <code>${CHANGE_ANAL=
YZER_MCP_SERVER_BASE_URL}/mcp</code></p>
<p local-id=3D"fabf674bc7e3"><strong>Source:</strong> <a class=3D"external-=
link" href=3D"https://source.datanerd.us/Alerting/change-analyzer" rel=3D"n=
ofollow">change-analyzer</a></p>
<p local-id=3D"cc5cef602359">All tools take an entity GUID + start time in =
epoch ms.</p>
<h3 local-id=3D"6d9166cc7c64" id=3D"id-2026-03-12SREAgentMCPServerTools-fet=
ch_deployment_metadata_analysis">fetch_deployment_metadata_analysis</h3>
<p local-id=3D"d0cd5bfc9edc">Examines change event data from the last 30 da=
ys to identify deviations from historical patterns.</p>
<ul local-id=3D"edfdce4a-9cb5-47b8-949f-f8ee75afeb70">
<li local-id=3D"c5f0a9a2-10f1-468d-a116-ee137a6351e5">
<p local-id=3D"4f05fd42efb8"><strong>Data source:</strong> NerdGraph =E2=80=
=94 Change Tracking API</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"33401807-726e-481c-ad31-22b92d26ee62">
<p local-id=3D"e5775e9148a8"><strong>URL:</strong> <code>${NERDGRAPH_BASE_U=
RI}/graphql</code> (default: <code>https://nerd-graph.staging-service.nr-op=
s.net/graphql</code>)</p></li>
</ul>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">query C=
hangeTrackingSearchQuery(
  $entityGuids: [EntityGuid!],
  $timeWindow: ChangeTrackingTimeWindowInputWithDefaults,
  $accountIds: [Int!],
  $limit: Int,
  $query: String,
  $nrdbEventTypes: [ChangeTrackingNrdbEventType!]
) {
  actor {
    changeTracking {
      changeTrackingSearch(filter: {
        entityGuids: $entityGuids,
        timeWindow: $timeWindow,
        accountIds: $accountIds,
        limit: $limit,
        query: $query,
        nrdbEventTypes: $nrdbEventTypes
      }) {
        changeEvents {
          ... on ChangeTrackingDeploymentEvent {
            changeTrackingId, timestamp, user, category, type, categoryAndT=
ype,
            description, shortDescription, changelog, commit, deepLink, gro=
upId,
            customAttributes,
            entity { guid, name, type, accountId }
          }
        }
      }
    }
  }
}
</pre>
</div>
</div>
<p local-id=3D"d9379a332f09">Query filter: <code>"eventType() =3D 'Deployme=
nt' OR (eventType() =3D 'ChangeTrackingEvent' AND category =3D 'Deployment'=
)"</code></p>
<hr local-id=3D"dba025f4-fd53-40b0-a69b-92e740e9c092">
<h3 local-id=3D"bf4fa5a94090" id=3D"id-2026-03-12SREAgentMCPServerTools-fet=
ch_performance_analysis">fetch_performance_analysis</h3>
<p local-id=3D"310223dc75c5">Golden metrics, transaction behavior, and infr=
astructure anomaly analysis around a change event.</p>
<p local-id=3D"9d795e8a9a38"><strong>Time window:</strong> 1 hour post-chan=
ge with 1 hour prior baseline</p>
<p local-id=3D"2ea0a75ae61d"></p>
<p local-id=3D"7f6e54270389">Calls multiple data sources:</p>
<p local-id=3D"1298e2918938"><strong>A. Golden Signals =E2=80=94 </strong><=
a class=3D"external-link" href=3D"https://source.datanerd.us/golden-signal-=
service" rel=3D"nofollow"><strong>golden-signal-service</strong></a><strong=
> (Thrift RPC)</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"865c7e6e-c8ed-4a82-b5a4-ba1cf6f657ba">
<li local-id=3D"df4d3ece-3536-4d0d-bb1d-2f3a1df8e5a4">
<p local-id=3D"a089a0d1fe07"><strong>URL:</strong> <code>${GOLDENSIGNALSTOR=
AGE_API_ENDPOINT}</code> (default: <code>https://staging-golden-signal-serv=
ice.vip.cf.nr-ops.net/golden_signal_service/v1</code>)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"3a26c48a-15c7-4fb8-b568-1ff45965db85">
<p local-id=3D"dac54f734b8d"><strong>Constraint:</strong> Last 90 minutes o=
nly; falls back to NRQL for older data</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"76f90d5f457a"><strong>B. Golden Signals fallback =E2=80=94 D=
irac (NRQL)</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"b95ffe18-2b47-49ef-b074-67e44112dd56">
<li local-id=3D"add2aa1f-27a9-4e80-8a55-a1ad7c8e1866">
<p local-id=3D"19f5ed325538"><strong>URL:</strong> <code>${DIRAC_BASE_URI}/=
api/1/query</code> (default: <code>https://nrql-query-gateway.staging-servi=
ce.nr-ops.net/api/1/query</code>)</p></li>
</ul>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">{golden=
_metric_definition} WHERE entity.guid =3D '{entity_guid}' SINCE {startTimeM=
s} UNTIL {endTimeMs}</pre>
</div>
</div>
<p local-id=3D"d7dddf45bdb5"><strong>C. Entity metadata =E2=80=94 NerdGraph=
</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"091569c1-12f5-4320-8860-2e6cafa4c40b">
<li local-id=3D"229827c4-3479-4328-833b-6df9f344a9e0">
<p local-id=3D"417970d22863"><strong>URL:</strong> <code>${NERDGRAPH_BASE_U=
RI}/graphql</code></p></li>
</ul>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">query E=
ntitiesQuery($guids: [EntityGuid]!) {
  actor {
    entities(guids: $guids) {
      accountId, domain, type, name, permalink, guid, alertSeverity
      goldenMetrics { metrics { name, metricName, definition { select, from=
, where } } }
      tags { key, values }
    }
  }
}
</pre>
</div>
</div>
<hr local-id=3D"e08973ea-1ff9-4256-a640-ac99b6461707">
<h3 local-id=3D"29f3245ea695" id=3D"id-2026-03-12SREAgentMCPServerTools-fet=
ch_alerts_analysis">fetch_alerts_analysis</h3>
<p local-id=3D"1379911fdb84">Examines alert incidents around a deployment t=
o determine if it triggered new alerts.</p>
<ul local-id=3D"2c9c83ef-f76b-450c-a9c8-7c4c65113df7">
<li local-id=3D"b0dc94ea-1661-46ef-883b-d38e57c64245">
<p local-id=3D"2614ca34e9ae"><strong>Data source:</strong> NerdGraph =E2=80=
=94 AI Issues Incidents API</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"a3aa9174-9525-4f95-b030-22dc2046ed1b">
<p local-id=3D"b758b2a1b20a"><strong>URL:</strong> <code>${NERDGRAPH_BASE_U=
RI}/graphql</code></p></li>
</ul>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">query A=
lertIncidents(
  $accountId: Int!,
  $incidentIds: [ID!],
  $entityGuids: [EntityGuid!],
  $startTime: EpochMilliseconds!,
  $endTime: EpochMilliseconds!,
  $cursor: String
) {
  actor {
    account(id: $accountId) {
      aiIssues {
        incidents(
          filter: { ids: $incidentIds, entityGuids: $entityGuids }
          timeWindow: { endTime: $endTime, startTime: $startTime }
          cursor: $cursor
        ) {
          incidents {
            incidentId, issueId, closedAt, createdAt, description,
            entityGuids, entityNames, entityTypes, priority, state,
            timestamp, updatedAt,
            account { id, name }
          }
          nextCursor
        }
      }
    }
  }
}
</pre>
</div>
</div>
<hr local-id=3D"a37290e1-3f1c-48c1-8d47-911773f7c8df">
<h2 local-id=3D"4ce6148f7e90" id=3D"id-2026-03-12SREAgentMCPServerTools-nr-=
mcp-server(ChangeEvents)">nr-mcp-server (Change Events)</h2>
<p local-id=3D"63b64c9cdae6"><strong>Config:</strong> <code>nrai_mcp_tool:v=
0.0.1.json</code></p>
<p local-id=3D"746434998fb3"><strong>Base URL:</strong> <code>${NR_MCP_SERV=
ER_MCP_URL}</code></p>
<p local-id=3D"41ecdfa20430"><strong>Source:</strong> <a class=3D"external-=
link" href=3D"https://source.datanerd.us/AIR/mcp-server/blob/master/src/new=
_relic_mcp/tools/basic_tools.py" rel=3D"nofollow">mcp-server/src/new_relic_=
mcp/tools/basic_tools.py</a></p>
<h3 local-id=3D"6a7afaf8e3f6" id=3D"id-2026-03-12SREAgentMCPServerTools-lis=
t_change_events">list_change_events</h3>
<p local-id=3D"b04d5f2cf493">Retrieves deployment and change event history =
for an entity.</p>
<ul local-id=3D"5c51d54e-3416-4483-9004-faaf92fe46c0">
<li local-id=3D"66bf54e9-ef50-4fb5-8c4b-db09da4e9c46">
<p local-id=3D"e6a0e9afe7c8"><strong>Data source:</strong> NerdGraph =E2=80=
=94 Change Tracking API</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"44e29db3-c153-475b-93f4-9afb37a2d0e8">
<p local-id=3D"b65efcd5d87c"><strong>URL:</strong> <code>${NERD_GRAPH_HOST}=
/graphql</code> (default: <code>https://api.newrelic.com/graphql</code>)</p=
></li>
<li local-id=3D"efda4a32-be9a-4281-9106-f2260495a5f9">
<p local-id=3D"d6af8752bd61"><strong>Query def:</strong> <code>queries.py</=
code></p></li>
</ul>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">query G=
etChangeTrackingEvents(
  $EntityGUIDs: [EntityGuid!]
  $StartTime: EpochMilliseconds!
  $EndTime: EpochMilliseconds!
  $NrdbEventTypes: [ChangeTrackingNrdbEventType!]
) {
  actor {
    changeTracking {
      changeTrackingSearch(
        filter: {
          entityGuids: $EntityGUIDs
          timeWindow: { startTime: $StartTime, endTime: $EndTime }
          nrdbEventTypes: $NrdbEventTypes
        }
      ) {
        changeEvents {
          category, categoryAndType, changeTrackingId, customAttributes,
          description, groupId, shortDescription, timestamp, type, user
          entity { guid, name }
          ... on ChangeTrackingDeploymentEvent { changelog, commit, deepLin=
k, version }
          ... on ChangeTrackingFeatureFlagEvent { featureFlagId }
        }
      }
    }
  }
}
</pre>
</div>
</div>
<p local-id=3D"438f5ef92529"><code>NrdbEventTypes</code> hardcoded as: <cod=
e>["CHANGE_TRACKING_EVENT", "DEPLOYMENT"]</code></p>
<hr local-id=3D"4cc0ed54-9cc0-445a-900f-bfda053ce0a8">
<h2 local-id=3D"017b2edfa384" id=3D"id-2026-03-12SREAgentMCPServerTools-nr-=
mcp-server(Mitigation)">nr-mcp-server (Mitigation)</h2>
<p local-id=3D"856346d9af10"><strong>Config:</strong> <code>nrai_mcp_mitiga=
tion_tool:v0.0.1.json</code></p>
<p local-id=3D"37d43003f00b"><strong>Base URL:</strong> <code>${NR_MCP_SERV=
ER_MCP_URL}</code></p>
<p local-id=3D"ced16f1d9892"><strong>Source:</strong> <a class=3D"external-=
link" href=3D"https://source.datanerd.us/AIR/mcp-server/blob/main/src/new_r=
elic_mcp/tools/declarative_tools_configs/" rel=3D"nofollow">mcp-server/src/=
new_relic_mcp/tools/declarative_tools_configs/</a></p>
<p local-id=3D"c80dbe1a5876"></p>
<h3 local-id=3D"456987e31336" id=3D"id-2026-03-12SREAgentMCPServerTools-ale=
rt_condition_recommendation_tool">alert_condition_recommendation_tool</h3>
<p local-id=3D"a70c41766ae7">Recommends alert conditions by entity domain/t=
ype with optional name or search filters.</p>
<ul local-id=3D"901c16af-d0c0-47da-aef3-0d592f97010d">
<li local-id=3D"92e17161-e150-4828-99d5-8d77f01347bf">
<p local-id=3D"a7b801de8f54"><strong>Data source:</strong> NerdGraph =E2=80=
=94 Alerts AskAI API</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"9c58465a-ca13-4f78-8b55-4935846c5344">
<p local-id=3D"4ef32e0cfe2d"><strong>URL:</strong> <code>${NERD_GRAPH_HOST}=
/graphql</code></p></li>
</ul>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">query G=
etRecommendedConditionsAskAi(
  $entity_domain: String,
  $entity_names: [String],
  $entity_type: String,
  $operator: String,
  $search_string: String
) {
  actor {
    account(id: {accountId}) {
      alerts {
        recommendConditionsAskAi(
          entityDomain: $entity_domain
          entityNames: $entity_names
          entityType: $entity_type
          operator: $operator
          searchString: $search_string
        ) {
          recommendations {
            card {
              actions { ... }
              body { ... }
              type, version
            }
          }
        }
      }
    }
  }
}
</pre>
</div>
</div>
<hr local-id=3D"423095bb-2077-4886-b369-519bdca5fe85">
<h3 local-id=3D"8c43291a7ba1" id=3D"id-2026-03-12SREAgentMCPServerTools-fet=
ch_alert_condition_recommendations">fetch_alert_condition_recommendations</=
h3>
<p local-id=3D"2b455d5ddcb5">Generates entity-specific alert condition reco=
mmendations with ready-to-use NRQL queries.</p>
<ul local-id=3D"ac60c250-7031-4ef9-af5d-8688034be1dc">
<li local-id=3D"2bfaa02b-3aec-497e-90ab-d647a4e8a929">
<p local-id=3D"9c4019ce46d3"><strong>Data source:</strong> NerdGraph =E2=80=
=94 Alerts Recommend Conditions API</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"08dbde76-1ef3-4fbe-a21c-d47c0353c3e0">
<p local-id=3D"73b4bf64812b"><strong>URL:</strong> <code>${NERD_GRAPH_HOST}=
/graphql</code></p></li>
</ul>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">query r=
ecommendConditions($accountId: Int!, $entityGuid: EntityGuid!) {
  actor {
    account(id: $accountId) {
      alerts {
        recommendConditions(recommend: { entityGuids: [$entityGuid] }) {
          recommendations {
            condition { name, nrql }
          }
        }
      }
    }
  }
}
</pre>
</div>
</div>
